          "action": "escalate_to_human",
          "handoffTarget": "noc_tier3_incident_commander",
          "rationale": "Storms of this size usually indicate a transport or power root cause masking child alarms; automated ticketing would flood the queue while the true fault ages — a human incident commander must take command and control."
        },
